high_descs: Turn right, go forward, turn left after the window
Pick up the knife on the counter
Turn left, go forward a bit, turn right in front of the basket
Cut the apple in the basket
Turn right, go forward a bit, turn left
Put the knife on the counter
Turn left, go forward a bit, turn right in front of the basket
Pick up an apple piece
Turn around, go forward a bit, turn left, go to the sink
Put the apple piece in the sink, open the water, wait, pick up the apple piece
Turn around, go forward, turn right in front of the window
Put the apple slice in the basket
anns.task_desc: Cut an apple, wash a piece of apple

high_descs: Walk forward then go right to get to the trash bin by the edge of the counter.
Pick up the knife from the counter.
Turn left, walk one step forward and look at the trash bin.
Chop up the apple inside the trash bin.
Turn right, walk one step forward and look at the counter.
Put the knife on top of the left side of the green sponge.
Turn left, walk one step forward and look at the trash bin.
Pick up the closest piece of chopped apple from the trash bin.
Turn around, then go left to the sink on the counter.
Put the apple slice in the sink, turn the water on, then turn it off and pick up the slice.
Turn around and walk over to face the spot on the ground just left of the trash bin.
Put the piece of apple in far back part of the trash bin.
anns.task_desc: Cut and wash a piece of apple, next put it back in the trash.

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the counter in between the gray bin on the floor and the stove on the left.
Pick up the knife from the left edge of the counter.
Turn left and walk to the gray bin on the floor on the right.
Slice the red apple inside the gray bin.
Turn right and walk to the counter on the left.
Put the knife down on the counter on top of the green sponge.
Turn left and walk to the gray bin on the floor on the right.
Pick up a slice of apple from the gray bin on the floor.
Turn around and walk to the sink on the left.
Put the slice of apple inside the sink, rinse it for a few seconds and pick it back up.
Turn around and walk to the gray bin on the floor to the right.
Put the rinsed slice of apple inside the gray bin.
anns.task_desc: Place a rinsed slice of apple in a gray bin.
